en_522817_0	Members of the Air Force, Police, Department of Forest and Wildlife, Government officials in the Pradeshiya Sabawa, Sigiriya and Urban Council-Dambulla, Hotel Associations of the area, Hoteliers, civil society activists and 53 Division troops launched a project to clean up either side of the road from Inamaluwa to Digampathana, covering about 4 km in length Sunday (9) and put up 20 awareness notice boards for protection of the environment along the road patch.
en_522817_1	The project was implemented by the General Officer Commanding Major General H.H.A.S.P.K Senarathne in collaboration with representatives of all those organizations.
